rows.label: qst300402_msg003
rows.name: タスク８クリア後テキスト

rows.label: qst300402_msg0001
rows.name:
Yew won't even tell me who this
latest job is from.

rows.label: qst300402_msg0002
rows.name:
He must really not be kidding
when he says they're a big shot.

rows.label: qst300402_msg0003
rows.name:
You'll let me know who it turns
out to be afterwards, right?
Just on the down low.

rows.label: qst300402_msg0101
rows.name:
Man, I can't believe your client
turned out to be the Queen herself!

rows.label: qst300402_msg0102
rows.name:
We had a mystery-client job to deal
with ourselves while you were gone,
you know. It was quite the challenge.
